sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant S as TCPServer
    participant P as ProtocolParser
    participant B as BrokerCore
    participant D as SegmentFile
    participant M as InMemoryLog

    C->>S: PRODUCE topic payload
    S->>P: parse_request(line)
    P-->>S: Request::Produce
    S->>B: produce(topic, message)
    B->>D: append_to_segment_file(...)
    B->>M: log.append(message)
    B-->>S: offset
    S-->>C: OK offset

    C->>S: FETCH topic offset
    S->>P: parse_request(line)
    P-->>S: Request::Fetch
    S->>B: fetch(topic, offset)
    B-->>S: Option<Message>
    S-->>C: MSG/NONE/ERR
